sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as 🖥️ Client
    participant API as 🔗 API FastAPI
    participant DB as 💾 MariaDB

    Note over Client,DB: 1️⃣ Créer Contact + Profil Relationnel

    Client->>API: POST /contacts
    API->>DB: INSERT Contact
    DB-->>API: contact_id (UUID)
    API-->>Client: 201 { id, nom, email ... }

    Client->>API: POST /contacts/{cid}/relationship-profile
    API->>DB: INSERT RelationshipProfile (contact_id FK)
    DB-->>API: profile_id
    API-->>Client: 201 { relationship_type, proximity_level ... }

    Note over Client,DB: 2️⃣ Enregistrer Interaction

    Client->>API: POST /contacts/{cid}/interactions
    API->>DB: INSERT Interaction (contact_id FK)
    DB-->>API: interaction_id
    API-->>Client: 201 { interaction_type, summary, detected_need ... }

    Note over Client,DB: 3️⃣ Créer Action de Suivi

    Client->>API: POST /contacts/{cid}/relationship-actions
    API->>DB: INSERT RelationshipAction (contact_id FK)
    DB-->>API: action_id
    API-->>Client: 201 { action_type, due_date, status=todo ... }

    Note over Client,DB: 4️⃣ Consulter Dashboard

    Client->>API: GET /rap/dashboard
    API->>DB: COUNT/AGGREGATE (all tables)
    DB-->>API: { due_today, overdue, active_relations, high_potential, recent_interactions }
    API-->>Client: 200 Dashboard Metrics

    Note over Client,DB: 5️⃣ Compléter Action

    Client->>API: PATCH /relationship-actions/{aid}/complete
    API->>DB: UPDATE status=done, completed_at=NOW()
    DB-->>API: updated action
    API-->>Client: 200 { status, completed_at ... }

    Note over Client,DB: 6️⃣ Supprimer Contact (Cascade)

    Client->>API: DELETE /contacts/{cid}
    API->>DB: DELETE Contact (cascade)
    DB->>DB: CASCADE DELETE RelationshipProfile
    DB->>DB: CASCADE DELETE Interactions
    DB->>DB: CASCADE DELETE RelationshipActions
    DB-->>API: 204 No Content
    API-->>Client: 204
